---

<MainLayout
  title="Cabinet Maker Murrieta, CA | Custom Kitchen Cabinets | First Class WoodWorks"
  description="Looking for a cabinet maker near me in Murrieta? First Class WoodWorks builds custom kitchen cabinets, bathroom vanities, and built-ins 100% in-house. 5-star rated. Serving Temecula Valley since day one."
>
  <Hero />

  <TrustBar />

  <Intro />
  
  <div class="w-full flex justify-center py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="w-64 h-[2px] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-zinc-300 to-transparent opacity-50"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Cabinet Maker Identity Section — GBP Category Match -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

        <div class="reveal">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
            Your Local <span class="text-yellow-600">Cabinet Maker</span> in Murrieta
          </h2>
          <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-yellow-600 rounded-full mb-8"></div>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            A cabinet maker is not a general contractor. A cabinet maker is not a handyman who installs pre-fab boxes.
