            from raw lumber — and that's exactly what First Class WoodWorks has done for every home we've touched
            in Murrieta, Temecula, and across Riverside County.
          </p>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
            When your Google search says "cabinet maker near me," you're looking for someone who knows the difference
            between a dovetail joint and a butt joint, between furniture-grade plywood and particle board,
            between a post-catalyzed conversion varnish and a can of paint from the hardware store.
            That's us. That's all we do.
          </p>
          <a href="/services/cabinet-maker" class="inline-block bg-zinc-900 text-white px-8 py-3 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs hover:bg-yellow-600 transition shadow-lg">
            What a Cabinet Maker Does
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal delay-200 bg-zinc-50 border border-zinc-200 rounded-sm p-8 md:p-10">
          <h3 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-zinc-500 mb-8">What Sets a True Cabinet Maker Apart</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-5">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="text-yellow-600 text-lg font-bold mt-0.5">01</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-1">Builds From Raw Lumber</p>
                <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm">We don't assemble flat-packs. We mill, join, and finish every component in our own shop.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="text-yellow-600 text-lg font-bold mt-0.5">02</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-1">Precision to the 1/16th Inch</p>
                <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm">Laser-measured and custom-scribed to your walls. No filler strips, no gaps, no compromise.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="text-yellow-600 text-lg font-bold mt-0.5">03</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-1">Traditional Joinery Methods</p>
                <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm">Dovetail drawer boxes and mortise-and-tenon face frames — the hallmark of heirloom cabinetry.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <span class="text-yellow-600 text-lg font-bold mt-0.5">04</span>
              <div>
                <p class="font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-1">Professional-Grade Finishing</p>
                <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm">Post-catalyzed conversion varnish applied in controlled conditions — not sprayed on-site.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Services />

  <RecentProjects />

  <AreasServed />

  <!-- Pricing Transparency & Custom vs Big Box Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white border-t border-zinc-100">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">

      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16 reveal">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-6 leading-tight">
