          Homeowners in Murrieta and Temecula often ask, "What should I budget for custom cabinets near me?"
          Here's what to expect when you invest in heirloom-quality cabinetry built by a local
          <a href="/services/custom-kitchen-cabinets" class="text-yellow-600 font-bold hover:underline">cabinet maker</a> — not a factory.
