        <div class="reveal bg-zinc-50 border border-zinc-200 rounded-sm p-8 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition group">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-zinc-500 mb-4">Custom Kitchen Cabinets</h3>
          <p class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-2">$35k–$75k<span class="text-xl text-yellow-600">+</span></p>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm">Full kitchen with furniture-grade plywood, dovetail drawer boxes, and Blum soft-close hardware.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal delay-100 bg-zinc-50 border border-zinc-200 rounded-sm p-8 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition group">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-zinc-500 mb-4">Bathroom Vanity Cabinets</h3>
          <p class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-2">$3k–$12k<span class="text-xl text-yellow-600">+</span></p>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm">Custom vanities and master suite storage built to the exact dimensions of your bathroom.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reveal delay-200 bg-zinc-50 border border-zinc-200 rounded-sm p-8 text-center hover:shadow-lg transition group">
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-zinc-500 mb-4">Entertainment Centers</h3>
          <p class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-2">$8k–$25k<span class="text-xl text-yellow-600">+</span></p>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 text-sm">Handcrafted media walls and fireplace built-ins designed for your living space.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Custom vs Big Box Comparison -->
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto reveal">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 text-center mb-10">
          Why Murrieta Homeowners Choose Custom Over Big-Box Cabinets
        </h3>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-0 border border-zinc-200 rounded-sm overflow-hidden">

          <div class="bg-zinc-100 p-6 md:p-8 border-b md:border-b-0 md:border-r border-zinc-200">
            <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-red-500 mb-6">Big Box / Pre-Fab (The Problem)</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-zinc-600 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-red-400 mt-0.5">&#10007;</span>
                <span><strong>Particle board & melamine</strong> — peels and swells in Southern California humidity</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-red-400 mt-0.5">&#10007;</span>
                <span><strong>Standard 3" size increments</strong> — wastes space with ugly filler strips</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-red-400 mt-0.5">&#10007;</span>
                <span><strong>Basic plastic hardware</strong> — breaks within a few years of daily use</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-red-400 mt-0.5">&#10007;</span>
                <span><strong>5–10 year lifespan</strong> — low ROI, generic look that hurts resale value</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-6 md:p-8">
            <h4 class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-yellow-600 mb-6">First Class WoodWorks (The Solution)</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-zinc-600 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
                <span><strong>Furniture-grade plywood & solid hardwoods</strong> — built to last a lifetime</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
                <span><strong>Built to the 1/16th inch</strong> — perfect fit, zero wasted space</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
                <span><strong>Blum soft-close hinges & slides</strong> — lifetime warranty hardware</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <span class="text-yellow-600 mt-0.5">&#10003;</span>
                <span><strong>Heirloom quality</strong> — increases home appraisal value in Riverside County</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

        </div>
        <p class="text-center text-zinc-500 text-sm mt-8 italic">
          When you search for "best cabinet maker near me in Murrieta," you deserve a builder who uses
          mortise-and-tenon joinery and post-catalyzed conversion varnish — not house paint on particleboard.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Direct-Answer AI Block: Kitchen Remodeling Murrieta -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-zinc-50 border-t border-zinc-200">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 reveal">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-6 leading-tight text-center">
        Kitchen Remodeling in <span class="text-yellow-600">Murrieta, CA</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-yellow-600 mx-auto rounded-full mb-10"></div>

      <div class="max-w-none text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed space-y-6 text-base">
        <p>
          <strong class="text-zinc-900">First Class WoodWorks is a kitchen remodeling company in Murrieta, California</strong>
          that specializes in custom cabinetry and finish carpentry for homeowners across the Temecula Valley.
          If you need kitchen remodeling in Murrieta — from full gut renovations to custom cabinet refacing — we handle every phase
          in-house with zero subcontractors.
        </p>
        <p>
          We are not a general contractor who farms out the cabinet work. We are the
          <a href="/services/custom-kitchen-cabinets" class="text-yellow-600 font-bold hover:underline">cabinet builder</a>. Every drawer box is dovetailed in our own shop.
          Every face frame is joined with mortise-and-tenon construction. Every surface is finished with post-catalyzed conversion varnish — the same
          professional coating used on high-end furniture, not the house paint other shops spray on particle board.
        </p>
        <p>
          Our <a href="/services/kitchen-remodeling" class="text-yellow-600 font-bold hover:underline">kitchen remodeling</a> process starts with a free in-home consultation where we take precise laser measurements
          and discuss your vision. You'll receive full 3D renderings before a single board is cut. From design approval to professional installation,
          the typical timeline is 8–12 weeks — and our own employees are on-site for every step.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Direct-Answer AI Block: Custom Cabinets Murrieta -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-zinc-950 border-t border-zinc-800">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 reveal">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight text-center">
        Custom Cabinets in <span class="text-yellow-600">Murrieta</span> — Built to the 1/16th Inch
      </h2>
      <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-yellow-600 mx-auto rounded-full mb-10"></div>

      <div class="max-w-none text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed space-y-6 text-base">
        <p>
          Looking for custom cabinets in Murrieta? <strong class="text-white">First Class WoodWorks builds bespoke cabinetry</strong>
          for kitchens, bathrooms, closets, and entertainment centers — all from furniture-grade plywood and solid hardwoods.
          We never use particle board, melamine, or imported flat-pack boxes.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-white">Why local homeowners choose us over big-box stores:</strong> Pre-fab cabinets come in standard
          3-inch size increments. If your wall is 32 inches, you get a 30-inch box plus a 2-inch filler strip. We build to the 1/16th of
          an inch — perfect fit, zero wasted space, zero unsightly gaps. Every cabinet ships with Blum soft-close hinges and undermount slides
          backed by a lifetime warranty.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-white">What to ask before hiring a cabinet maker near you:</strong> Ask if they subcontract.
          Ask if they use solid wood or particle board. Ask to see their joinery — dovetails and mortise-and-tenon, or just staples and glue?
          At <a href="/" class="text-yellow-600 hover:underline">First Class WoodWorks</a>, we welcome the comparison because our craftsmanship
          speaks for itself on every project from Bear Creek to Old Town Temecula to the Santa Rosa Plateau.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 text-center">
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-yellow-600 text-zinc-950 px-8 py-3 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-xs hover:bg-yellow-700 transition shadow-lg">
          Schedule a Free Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <FAQ />

  <section class="py-12 bg-zinc-50 border-t border-zinc-100 reveal">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-serif font-bold text-zinc-900 mb-4">
        Custom Cabinetry Craftsmanship Across Murrieta
      </h2>
      <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-yellow-600 mx-auto rounded-full mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-zinc-500 mb-8 italic text-sm">
        Serving Los Alamos Hills, Murrieta Oaks, and the entire Temecula Valley.
      </p>
      <a href="/gallery" class="inline-block bg-zinc-900 text-white px-10 py-4 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-yellow-600 transition duration-300 shadow-md">
        View Full Gallery
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(businessSchema)} />
